data.description: It is almost impossible to find a 5-bedroom, 4-full bath, 3600 square foot home for this price, but 113 Windsor Creek Court is the ONE!  This beautiful home is located in the desirable Windsor Creek Subdivision. As you enter, you'll be immediately drawn to the open floor plan that encompasses a formal den or office, a spacious dining room, an expansive great room, and a main level bedroom and full bath room. The great room features a cozy gas fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for all your entertaining needs.    Adjacent to the great room, you'll find a large kitchen equipped with an abundance of cabinets to store your kitchen gadgets, and stunning granite countertops that provide ample room for preparing your favorite meals. The kitchen effortlessly flows into the breakfast area, creating a cozy spot for casual dining.    As you ascend to the upper level, you'll discover a media room prewired for audio-visual entertainment, offering endless possibilities for movie nights or immersive gaming experiences. The grand master suite is sure to impress, boasting an amazing master bath and two incredible walk-in closets, providing both luxury and functionality. The second level also houses three additional bedrooms, one of which has its own private bathroom, while another conveniently connects to the hall bath.    This home is a true gem, combining style, comfort, and practicality to cater to your every need.
